title: Age of Empires Gold.iso
description:
As the giuding spirit of a Stone Age tribe, follow one of these paths to build the greatest civilization on earth.

Experience all of the conflict, intrigue, greed, and power as you create the most feared and celebrated civilization in history.

The Roman Empire.

Creadted by the developers of the award-winning real-yime strategy game, Age of Empires, The Rise of Rome lets you plat an active role in directing the ascension of the infamous Roman Empire.

From the Stone Age to the Age of Iron, you have over 10,000 years of real-time evolution to build your tribe into a flourishing empire.

A fully intergrated scenario editor lets you create you own historically based conflicts.

Choose from 16 civilisations ( including 4 new civilisations ), with the unique technology trees and distinct strengths and weaknesses.

Minimum System Requirements:

Windows 98, ME, XP
Processor: P120 Mhz
Sytem Memory: 16 MB
Graphicd Card: 1MB
Sound: DX Compatible
DirectX: 5 or Higher
CD-Rom: 4 Speed
Free Hard Disk Space: 230 MB
